<h3>
   The CHEVIE package
</h3>
<p>
  Share package since release 3.4, April 1997. (This has superseded the
  <mixer var="GAP3"/> share package <a href="weyl.html">"weyl"</a>.)<br />
  CHEVIE has not yet been transferred to or replaced in
  <mixer var="GAP4"/>. You can use it only in <mixer var="GAP3"/>.
</p>

